clifford 's really big movie is an american animated epic adventure comedy-drama family film , loosely based on the book series clifford the big red dog by norman &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and more closely based on the classic pbs kids tv series adapted from it . this film was directed by robert ramirez , produced by scholastic entertainment and big red dog productions , and originally released to theaters by warner bros. on february 20 , 2004 . the film depicts a labrador retriever named clifford ( john ritter ) running away and joining a travelling animal show known as " larry 's amazing animals " with his best friends . larry &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( judge reinhold ) , the presenter of the animal show , does n't allow animals who have owners , so they pretend their dog tags are fake . the film takes place in the fictional island of " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; island " , which is the name is inspired by norman &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , the author of the books . this was john ritter 's final film role as he died of &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; dissection on september 11 , 2003 . the film was dedicated to his memory , and it serves as the series finale .